Pattern analysis commands

Usage: do-memory-cli pattern <COMMAND>

Commands:
  list           List patterns
  view           View pattern details
  analyze        Analyze pattern effectiveness
  search         Search for patterns semantically similar to a query
  recommend      Recommend patterns for a specific task
  effectiveness  Show pattern effectiveness rankings
  decay          Apply pattern decay
  batch          Batch pattern operations (4-6x faster)
  help           Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
